                    <li>Allows Couples</li>
                    <li>Geyser</li>
                    <li>TV</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-to-book">
            <h2>
                How To Book?
            </h2>
            <div>
                <img src="https://www.hotel-west-end.com/img/photos/b/57d2784f362dbb873d181d83908fdc05.jpg" alt="room" />
                <p>
                    Travel is a wonderful experience for most people who embark on a journey from one place to another.
                    One of the essential aspects of travelling
                    to a new place includes booking a hotel room in advance while planning the journey.
                    Nowadays, it is easy to just book hotel rooms online in a
                    convenient way.<br /><br />
                    Steps to book room in the OHMS hotel :<br />
                    1. Click on the 'Book Room' option in the Header. <br />
                    2. Enter your desired dates on the landing page.<br />
                    3. It will provide you all the available room types in our Hotel.<br />
                    4. To book a certain type of room, click on the link provided next to it. <br />
                    5. Provide your personal details on the landing page.<br />
                    6. Click on 'Book' to confirm your booking.<br />
                    7. Hurrray! Booking Made...We will wait for your arrival.<br />
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h2 style="margin-top: 5rem;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        color: #1d3557;
        font-size: 2.5em;
        font-weight: 500;
        line-height: .7em;
